Frequently Asked Questions

Quick answers to common questions. Can't find what you're looking for? Contact us above.

How do I enroll in a course?

Simply browse our course catalog, select the course you're interested in, and click "Enroll Now". You can pay securely and start learning immediately.

Do you offer certificates?

Yes! Most of our courses offer certificates of completion. You'll receive your certificate after successfully completing all course requirements.

Can I get a refund?

We offer a 30-day money-back guarantee on all paid courses. If you're not satisfied, contact our support team for a full refund.

How long do I have access?

Once you enroll in a course, you have lifetime access to all course materials, including future updates and additional content.
